test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[990], [990], [990]]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: [990]
  Full diff:
  - [[990], [990], [990]]
  + []
test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[990]]
  Right contains one more item: [990]
  Full diff:
  - [[990]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 178200 == 990
 +  where 178200 = <built-in function prod>([1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 9, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
